Stun Grenades$Less-lethal bursts that shock and stagger nearby foes. Buy seconds to reload, chainsaw, or reposition without relying on raw damage.$StunGrenadeAmmo$Charge type: throwable ammo#
Shield Grenades$A protective grenade package that throws up barrier-style coverage. Use it when you need breathing room in open arenas or while reviving a risky push.$ShieldGrenadeAmmo$Charge type: throwable ammo#
Void Grenades$Experimental ordnance that tears at whatever physics the invasion runs on. Toss into packs for disruptive burst damage and chaos.$VoidGrenadeAmmo$Charge type: throwable ammo#
